N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 200.11 - Form of abstract

State Regulations

The abstract of vouchers rendered shall show the balance of
cash on hand as per previous statement, the collections received since the last
statement, the interest on the bank balance, any miscellaneous receipts, a
deduction for vouchers itemized in the schedule and the balance remaining on
hand. Notes
